{"tid":130913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[美容黑店][laser]= 暗瘡jj中大伏","createTime":"2017-02-22T16:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T03:06:31.000Z","uid":66422,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f03615551a5a7c9e6fcab831b09719f113942963","tid":130913,"uid":66422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T16:49:33.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲上過旺角間hydro beauty做laser facial?<br />\n本身自己有瘡印同好多石頭瘡想做laser,<br />\n上左去同佢講我敏感皮膚 想淨係局部做,<br />\n佢就話laser係專for敏感皮膚做<br />\n咁我又on9又柒咁信左 就全面做<br />\n<br />\n做完無乜野 過左幾個鐘開始痕又紅<br />\n而加全面敏感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問有無呢間野嘅苦主 或者做過laser嘅人一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲哄左我落訂做千五蚊嘅package 我話我户口得番一百蚊 (廢事佢sell我)佢都話照收 結果千五蚊嘅野 真係收左一百蚊訂金...真係一毫子都笠盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2001d01cdf68e73b95e9dfaeec7e2a93b724d0","tid":130913,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"唔係有冷靜期咩？"},{"pid":"3bc5e5351cc84fd44d27fc2edbd24c079ba4c118","tid":130913,"uid":66422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係有冷靜期咩？</blockquote><br />\n佢話做完就得 唔會泛紅 即刻出得街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babe6ec5cd2c216f0f28afc7728a9903a30f53d4","tid":130913,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:12:00.000Z","msg":"一百蚊既功夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7ce7b80f78a3df94a18652712af79b62c6fbf3","tid":130913,"uid":66422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一百蚊既功夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只係個package嘅訂金係一百蚊<br />\n打一次laser係二百幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hk